# Path prefixes exempt from the check-typography action.
#
# The original rationale (staying byte-identical to upstream
# whg517/browser-bridge for clean merges) ended with the rebrand to
# chromium-bridge (ADR-0023). This list now only holds files that a later
# rebuild phase converts to plain ASCII, and it must only ever shrink:
# - src/apps/extension/: converted with the Phase 7 extension rehaul.
# - src/apps/desktop/ui/src/locales/: the desktop app's zh bundles (and the
#   native-language-names constants), legitimately CJK - the same category as
#   the extension's locale files, policed by scripts/check-cjk.ts.
# - docs/ and README.md: Chinese-language docs owned by the translation
#   pass; historical ADRs keep their original text. Cleaned in Phase 11.
# - CHANGELOG.md: generated release history, never edited by hand.
src/apps/extension/
src/apps/desktop/ui/src/locales/
src/apps/desktop/ui/src/lib/native-language-names.ts
docs/
CHANGELOG.md
